high_descs: Turn left and go to the white table to the right of the refrigerator.
Pick up the kettle on the right hand side of the white table.
Turn left and move to the sink on the other end of the kitchen.
Place the kettle in the sink and fill/rinse the kettle in water and pick it back up.
Turn around and go back to the white table to the right of the refrigerator.
Place the kettle to the left of the sponge on the white table.
anns.task_desc: Fill or rinse the kettle on the white table with water and put it back.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the right side of the white table.
Pick up the metal kettle on the right side of the table.
Turn left and walk to the sink.
Wash the kettle in the sink.
Turn around and veer left back to the table.
Place the kettle on the table to the left of the sponge.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean kettle on a table.

high_descs: Turn left, take a step, turn right, walk to the end of the table, turn left, walk to the other table.
Pick up the tea kettle on the rear right corner of the table behind the green sponge.
Turn completely around, move slightly forward, turn right and walk to the sink.
Put the tea kettle in the sink, fill the sink with water, drain the water, pick up the tea kettle.
Turn completely around, walk to the middle of the two tables, turn left and take a step toward the table.
Put the tea kettle on the table left of the green sponge.
anns.task_desc: Rinse the tea kettle and put it back on the table it was on.
